<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.8.1">
<l>tiripura mūṉṟerit tāṉumaṟṟai malarmicai mēlaya ṉumviyappa</l>
<l>muritirai mākaṭal pōlmuḻaṅki mūvula kummuṟai yālvaṇaṅka</l>
<l>veriyaṉa kēcara vāḷeyiṟṟō ṭiraṇiya ṉākami raṇṭukūṟā</l>
<l>variyuru vāmiva rārkkoleṉṉa vaṭṭapu yakarat tēṉeṉṟārē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When I asked, “Who is this who became a lion [in] form with sharp teeth</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] a fire-like mane, roaring like the great ocean with curling waves,</l>
<l>So that Hiraṇya’s chest became two parts, while the one</l>
<l rend="indent">who set fire to Trīpura</l>
<l>As well as the unborn on the lotus were amazed, [and] as the three worlds</l>
<l rend="indent">adored him by turns?”</l>
<l>He answered, “I am he in the house of the eight-armed [lord].”</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
